<!DOCTYPE html>
<html
  lang="ar"
  dir="rtl"
>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta
      name="Description"
      content="يتيح لك العثور على أفضل المدن لزيارتها في محيطك الجغرافي ؛ يمكنك العثور بسهولة على مكان لقظاء إجازة شتوية أكثر دفئًا أو رحلة صيفية أكثر برودة."
    />
    <title>WeatherVenue</title>
    <script src="https://polyfill.io/v3/polyfill.min.js?features=default"></script>
    <script
      src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"
      integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      integrity="sha384-JcKb8q3iqJ61gNV9KGb8thSsNjpSL0n8PARn9HuZOnIxN0hoP+VmmDGMN5t9UJ0Z"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <script
      src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-B4gt1jrGC7Jh4AgTPSdUtOBvfO8shuf57BaghqFfPlYxofvL8/KUEfYiJOMMV+rV"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <script
      src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyBcL91cr-kioveamPxcvnQTT4OA9asC1TE&callback=initMap&libraries=places&v=weekly"
      centerLocation="algiers"
      lang="ar"
      defer
    ></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="./css/style.css" />
    <script src="./js/cookies-eu-banner.js"></script>
    <script
      src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/screenfull.js/5.1.0/screenfull.min.js"
      integrity="sha512-SGPHIoS+NsP1NUL5RohNpDs44JlF36tXLN6H3Cw+EUyenEc5zPXWqfw9D+xmvR00QYUYewQIJQ6P5yH82Vw6Fg=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="cookies-eu-banner" style="display: none">
      مع الاستمرار في زيارة هذا الموقع ، فإنك تقبل استخدام ملفات تعريف الارتباط
      (cookies) بواسطة Google Analytics لأغراض إحصائية.
      <a
        href="https://www.google.ae/intl/ar/about/company/user-consent-policy-help/"
        id="cookies-eu-more"
        >اقرأ التفاصيل</a
      >
      <button id="cookies-eu-reject">لا أوافق</button>
      <button id="cookies-eu-accept">أوافق</button>
    </div>
    <div id="spinner-back"></div>
    <div id="spinner-front"><img src="./img/loading.gif" /><br /></div>

    <%- include("partials/header_ar.ejs") %> 
    <%- include("partials/disclaimer_modal_ar.ejs") %>
    <%- include("partials/weather_alert_panel.ejs") %>

    <!-- this block can float in code, order doesnt matter -->
    <input
      id="pac-input"
      class="controls"
      type="text"
      placeholder="أدخل موقعًا"
    />
    <div id="infowindow-content">
      <span id="place-name" class="title"></span><br />
      <span id="place-address"></span>
    </div>
    <!--this block can float in code, order doesnt matter -->
    <div class="empty-space bg-white" style="width: 100%;">
      <h3 id="location">
        ستظهر هنا تنبآت الطقس لمدة أسبوع. يمكنك اختيار المدن المجاورة من الخريطة
      </h3>
      <p id="date"></p>
    </div>
    <div class="h-100 w-100">
      <div id="map" style="width: 100%; height: 100%"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-fluid">
      <div class="row" id="forecast-items"></div>
    </div>

    <section id="imgGrid"></section>
    <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>

  </body>
  <script src="./js/js_variables.js"></script>
  <script src="./js/GMap.js"></script>
  <script src="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js?render=6LePZnQaAAAAACdKiEKOMZapuQLaP7BsulHobPQn"></script>
  <script>
    new CookiesEuBanner(function () {
      // Your code to launch when user accept cookies
      // Google Analytics code goes here.
      console.log("accepted");
    });
    fullScreenBtn = document.getElementById("fullscreen");
    fullScreenBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
      if (screenfull.isEnabled) {
        screenfull.request();
      } else {
        // Ignore or do something else
      }
    });
    screenfull.on("change", () => {
      screenfull.isFullscreen
        ? (fullScreenBtn.style.visibility = "hidden")
        : (fullScreenBtn.style.visibility = "visible");
    });
  </script>
</html>
